 been utter trash under Trump and the republicans. Where\u2019s our infrastructure bills? At least under sleepy joe we passed infrastructure and invested locally, instead now we want $1.5 trilllion to feed the war machine? Yeah fuck that and fuck this surveillance state ID verification nonsense they\u2019re passing to try and de-anonymize the internet.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 29, "score_up": 17, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZf5sMuC", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 14, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8592624, "raw_content": "", "author": "HeNotMedicated", "created": 1777611768818, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Calumet57", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZf5sMuC.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/w6Ai8s1D0rdV.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/6E7wUfBi6fIuOr7E.jpeg", "width": 768, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 516}], "blurhash": "UNI}q+rqWXoz.Ax^WVRP~on,jYR+M*IUt6xv", "full_resolution": [784, 1168]}, "title": "The Truth about THE DEEP STATE is simpler then you may think.", "last_comment_created": 1777614449933, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 2, "score_up": 14, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 